# Default: treat as text, force LF on checkout (prevents Windows editors
# from sneaking CRLF back into the repo).
* text=auto eol=lf

# Windows-only scripts: keep the repository's CRLF bytes as-is so
# PowerShell / cmd.exe handle them correctly and Git does not create
# noisy EOL-only diffs for existing CRLF script files.
*.ps1 -text
*.cmd -text
*.bat -text

# Pre-built binary artifacts: never touch line endings.
dist_beta/* binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.pdf binary

# Vendored third-party source: leave as-is.
vendor/** -text
